---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const STRIPE_LINK = 'https://buy.stripe.com/aFa5kwag8eYm1TC2nAe3e00';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Polaris Stack Audit — Your AI Tool Stack, Optimised in 48 Hours"
  description="Stop paying for AI tools you don't need. Get a personalised Loom walkthrough + one-page PDF audit of your exact stack in 48 hours. $197, one payment, no Zoom calls."
  canonicalUrl="https://toolpolaris.com/stack-audit/"
>

  <style>
    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      background: var(--brand-dark);
      padding: 100px 0 80px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .hero-eyebrow {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1.6px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--brand-accent);
      background: rgba(245,166,35,0.12);
      padding: 5px 14px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      line-height: 1.1;
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto 16px;
    }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto 36px;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .hero-meta {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      margin-top: 16px;
    }
    .hero-badges {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
    .badge {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    }
    .badge-icon {
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
      background: var(--brand-accent);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: var(--brand-dark);
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    /* ── PROBLEM BLOCK ── */
    .problem {
      padding: 80px 0;
      background: #fff;
    }
    .problem-inner {
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .problem h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .problem p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: #444;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .problem p strong {
      color: var(--brand-dark);
    }

    /* ── HOW IT WORKS ── */
    .how {
      background: var(--brand-light);
      padding: 80px 0;
    }
    .how h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .steps {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 28px;
    }
    .step {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 32px 28px;
      border: 1px solid #e8ecf4;
    }
    .step-num {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      background: var(--brand-dark);
      color: var(--brand-accent);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .step h3 {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: var(--brand-dark);
    }
    .step p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* ── WHAT YOU GET ── */
    .deliverables {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 80px 0;
    }
    .deliverables h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .deliverables-sub {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .checklist {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
      max-width: 640px;
    }
    .checklist li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 14px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .check {
      width: 22px;
      height: 22px;
      background: var(--brand-accent);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--brand-dark);
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }
    .not-included {
      margin-top: 28px;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      padding: 14px 18px;
      background: #f9f9f7;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border-left: 3px solid #ddd;
      max-width: 640px;
    }

    /* ── WHO IT'S FOR ── */
    .who {
      background: var(--brand-light);
      padding: 80px 0;
    }
    .who h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .who-list {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 14px;
      max-width: 640px;
    }
    .who-list li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .who-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      background: var(--brand-accent);
      border-radius: 50%;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    /* ── FAQ ── */
    .faq {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 80px 0;
    }
    .faq h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .faq-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 32px;
      max-width: 680px;
    }
    .faq-item h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--brand-dark);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .faq-item p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #444;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    /* ── FINAL CTA ── */
    .final-cta {
      background: var(--brand-dark);
      padding: 100px 0;
      text-align: center;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .final-cta h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    }
    .final-cta p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      margin-bottom: 36px;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
    .final-meta {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
      margin-top: 18px;
    }
    .guarantee-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 24px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      border-radius: 30px;
      padding: 8px 20px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero { padding: 64px 0 56px; }
    }
  </style>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════
       HERO
  ═══════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Polaris Stack Audit</span>
      <h1>Your AI tool stack,<br/>audited and optimised.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        48-hour turnaround. One payment. No Zoom calls.
      </p>
      <a href={STRIPE_LINK} class="btn-primary" style="font-size:1.05rem;padding:16px 36px;">
        Get My Stack Audit — $197 &rarr;
      </a>
      <p class="hero-meta">Delivered as a Loom walkthrough + one-page PDF</p>
      <div class="hero-badges">
        <div class="badge"><div class="badge-icon">✓</div> 48-hour delivery</div>
        <div class="badge"><div class="badge-icon">✓</div> One payment, no subscription</div>
        <div class="badge"><div class="badge-icon">✓</div> 30-day money-back guarantee</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════
       PROBLEM
  ═══════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="problem">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="problem-inner">
        <h2>You're paying for six, seven, maybe eight AI subscriptions.</h2>
        <p>
          And if you're being honest, you couldn't tell someone off the top of your head what each one actually does for your business.
        </p>
        <p>
          That's not a character flaw. It's the predictable result of a market that releases a "game-changing" new tool every two weeks, combined with a work schedule that doesn't leave room to actually evaluate anything properly.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>The Polaris Stack Audit is how you fix that</strong> — without spending another 15 hours in YouTube rabbit holes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════
       HOW IT WORKS
  ═══════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="how">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Here's how it works</h2>
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">1</div>
          <h3>You fill out a short intake form</h3>
          <p>Tell us your current tool stack, what services you sell, how your week actually looks, and where you feel most inefficient. Specific answers get specific recommendations — vague answers get vague ones.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">2</div>
          <h3>We audit your stack</h3>
          <p>Within 48 hours, we review everything you've told us against the current AI tools landscape for marketing professionals. We identify what's redundant, what's missing, and how to connect it all into a workflow that actually saves you time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">3</div>
          <h3>You get a Loom + a one-pager</h3>
          <p>A 15–20 minute personalised Loom walkthrough explaining exactly what we'd cut, what we'd keep, and what 1–2 tools you're missing. Plus a one-page PDF with the same recommendations in scannable form — designed to be saved, not just watched once and forgotten.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════
       WHAT'S INCLUDED
  ═══════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="deliverables">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What's included</h2>
      <p class="deliverables-sub">Everything you need to go from "I think I'm wasting money" to a leaner, faster stack.</p>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li>
          <div class="check">✓</div>
          <span><strong>Personal Loom walkthrough (15–20 min)</strong> — your specific tools, your specific workflow, zero generic advice</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="check">✓</div>
          <span><strong>One-page PDF summary</strong> — cut / keep / add, with brief rationale for each recommendation</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="check">✓</div>
          <span><strong>Stack connection guide</strong> — how your recommended tools talk to each other</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="check">✓</div>
          <span><strong>Suggested weekly workflow</strong> — what your new, leaner setup actually looks like in practice</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="not-included">
        <strong>Not included:</strong> upsells, retainer pitches, or vague consulting hedging.
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════
       WHO IT'S FOR
  ═══════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="who">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Who this is for</h2>
      <ul class="who-list">
        <li>
          <div class="who-dot"></div>
          <span>Solo marketing consultants and freelancers running 3–8 clients who don't have time to evaluate tools properly</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="who-dot"></div>
          <span>People who've accumulated 6–12 subscriptions and aren't confident all of them are earning their keep</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="who-dot"></div>
          <span>Professionals who suspect they're doing things the slow way but don't know what "the fast way" actually looks like</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="who-dot"></div>
          <span>Anyone who has spent real money on AI tools and couldn't honestly describe the ROI of at least half of them</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════
       FAQ
  ═══════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="faq">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Common questions</h2>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>"$197 seems like a lot for a 48-hour turnaround."</h3>
          <p>
            The average solo marketing consultant in our audience spends $250–$400/month on SaaS tools. If we identify one redundant $30/month subscription you can cancel — which we almost always do — this audit pays for itself in 6 months. If we identify two or three, you're ahead inside 60 days. And that's before counting the time you'll save on a leaner workflow.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>"Can't I just do this myself?"</h3>
          <p>
            You could. Evaluating 10+ tools properly — reading reviews, watching demos, understanding how they connect, comparing alternatives — takes 15–25 hours. If you bill at $75/hour, that's $1,125–$1,875 of your time. You're here because you haven't done it, despite knowing you should. This is the version where it actually gets done.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>"What if I'm not happy with the audit?"</h3>
          <p>
            30-day money-back guarantee, no questions asked. Request a refund via email and we'll process it same day.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════
       FINAL CTA
  ═══════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="final-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to stop guessing?</h2>
      <p>$197 — one payment, 48-hour delivery.</p>
      <a href={STRIPE_LINK} class="btn-primary" style="font-size:1.1rem;padding:18px 40px;">
        Get My Stack Audit &rarr;
      </a>
      <p class="final-meta">
        Delivered within 48 hours of completing your intake form.
      </p>
      <div class="guarantee-badge">
        🛡️ 30-day money-back guarantee — no questions asked
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
